---
title: Beyond Meat® Burgers and Greek-Style Salad with Feta Mayo
description: The dribble-down-your-chin simplicity of the noble burger can be reinvented time and time again to create the best dinnertime results. For this version, we've put a Greek-inspired twist on it with feta cheese and tomato salad!
